headline: Expedia Group to Participate in Morgan Stanley’s 2026 TMT Conference
summary: SEATTLE, February 24, 2026--Expedia Group (NASDAQ: EXPE) will participate in Morgan Stanley’s 2026 Technology, Media & Telecom Conference. Scott Schenkel, Chief Financial Officer, will participate in a fireside chat on Tuesday, March 3, 2026 at 10:00 am PT / 1:00 pm ET.
